dcterms:description: The dataset contains hourly air quality data from an Italian city, with 12 attributes and 1000 instances corresponding to measurements made between February 21, 2005, and April 4, 2005. The target attribute to predict is N OX.
dcterms:title: Italian city air quality dataset

dcterms:description: This dataset corresponds to daily air quality measurements from a monitoring station located in Lorca, Spain. It contains 10 attributes and 1000 instances collected between April 7, 2019, and December 31, 2021, with the target attribute being N O2.
dcterms:title: Lorca air quality dataset
